---
title: Double Sticky Chinese-Style Pork Noodles with Sweet Chilli-Oyster Veggies & Parsley
description: The perfect sauce is here, so make room in your pan (and your stomach!) for this Chinese-style dish where pork, veggies and udonnnoodles take centre stage. With a sprinkling of fresh parsley for a boost of flavour, you’ll be slurping your way to noodle nirvana in no time!

*We’ve replaced the pea pods in this recipe with green beans due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just
follow your recipe card!*
